  "id": "RAW_52796099",
  "title": "只能留一个！亏不起的保时捷，被迫在 Panamera 与 Taycan 间「二选一」",
  "url": "https://www.ifanr.com/1657524?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=",
  "date": "2026-03-10 18:17:08",
  "author": "芥末",
  "siteName": "爱范儿",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>2019 年 9 月，保时捷 Taycan 的全球首秀在三个大洲同时拉开帷幕。</p>\n  <p>在加拿大尼亚加拉瀑布的水力发电站，巨大的水雾冲天而起，震耳欲聋的轰鸣声展示着自然界最原始的重力势能；在德国新哈登贝格广袤的太阳能农场，数万块矩阵排列的硅晶面板正静默地吞噬着刺眼的强光；而在中国福建平潭岛的海岸线上，百米高的巨大风力发电机叶片正裹挟着咸湿的海风，发出沉闷而有节奏的呼啸。</p>\n  <p>保时捷极其罕见地跨越三大洲，用风、光、水三种最庞大也最纯粹的清洁能源，为旗下首款纯电动跑车搭建了宏大的舞台。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657525\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-6.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1172\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-6.png!720 2048w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-6-360x206.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-6-768x440.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/1-6-1024x586.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\"></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲ 位于福建的发布会舞台</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>当那台姿态极度低趴的 Taycan 悄无声息地滑入聚光灯下时，保时捷百年来标志性的水平对置排气声浪，被一种高频且充满未来感的微弱电流声所取代。</p>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 27px 0px;padding: 0px 15px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-align: justify;line-height: 25px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">这一刻的视觉冲击力极强，Taycan 就像是斯图加特向旧时代递出的一封优雅但决绝的战书。</span></p>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 27px 0px;padding: 0px 15px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-align: justify;line-height: 25px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">随后的市场反馈也印证了这一步的成功，2021 年，Taycan 的销量一度超越了保时捷的灵魂车型 911。</span></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657526\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-5.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2724\" height=\"1568\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-5.png!720 2724w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-5-360x207.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-5-768x442.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/2-5-1024x589.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2724px) 100vw, 2724px\"></p>\n  <p>在这种荣光下，直到 2024 年初，保时捷 Taycan 产品线副总裁 Kevin Giek 在接受采访时依然笃定地表示，Taycan 是一个「长期存在」的车型名称，其战略地位与 911 齐平。</p>\n  <p>然而，商业世界的剧本变化的往往比发布会上的光影魔术更快。</p>\n  <h2>急转弯</h2>\n  <p>当时间来到 2026 年初，在连续两年跌跌不休的纯电车型销量数据和难看的财务报表面前，保时捷管理层不得不开始评估一个在两年前无法想象的决策——</p>\n  <p><strong>剥离 Taycan 的独立地位，将其并入 Panamera 产品线，整合为一条统一的高性能四门轿车系列。</strong></p>\n  <p>Taycan 和 Panamera 目前是两套完全独立运作的产品项目，虽然定位相近，但在工程层面二者几乎没有重叠之处。</p>\n  <p>目前的 Panamera 基于大众集团成熟的 MSB 平台打造，按照保时捷原本的路线，第三代 Panamera 将在本十年内平滑过渡到更新的 PPC 高级燃油平台，继续以燃油和插电式混合动力作为主力销售引擎。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657527\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-6.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2724\" height=\"1568\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-6.png!720 2724w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-6-360x207.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-6-768x442.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/3-6-1024x589.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2724px) 100vw, 2724px\"></p>\n  <p>而 Taycan 则是基于专为高性能纯电车型开发的 J1 平台打造，在集团内部与奥迪 e-tron GT 共享这套昂贵的底层架构。按照原计划，Taycan 的继任车型理应顺利切入大众集团最新一代的 SSP Sport 纯电平台，完成电气化技术的迭代。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657528\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-5.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2724\" height=\"1568\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-5.png!720 2724w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-5-360x207.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-5-768x442.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/4-5-1024x589.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2724px) 100vw, 2724px\"></p>\n  <p>在宏观经济向好、纯电车型销量狂飙突进的时代，保时捷依靠超高的单车利润，尚能从容地支撑这两套完全独立的研发体系、两套互不兼容的零部件供应链以及两组并行的工程团队。</p>\n  <p>但随着市场情绪回落，销量下跌，维持这种「双轨制」的成本开始变得无法承受。</p>\n  <p>2025 年全年，Taycan 的全球交付量回落至 16339 辆，而同期的 Panamera 依然稳扎稳打，交出了 27701 辆的成绩单。</p>\n  <p>在纯电车型销量规模明显收缩的当下，继续为一款年销不足两万台的车型单独维持一条昂贵且庞大的底层平台迭代路径，已经变得不再划算。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657529\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-5.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2724\" height=\"1568\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-5.png!720 2724w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-5-360x207.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-5-768x442.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/5-5-1024x589.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2724px) 100vw, 2724px\"></p>\n  <p>大众集团内部的软件架构危机则则使局面雪上加霜。由于 CARIAD 软件部门的持续动荡和重组，直接导致了原定于近年推出的 SSP Sport 纯电平台遭遇了严重的研发延期。</p>\n  <p>底层架构的难产，使得保时捷前期投入的巨额研发资金面临极高的沉没风险，公司因此被迫在财报中计提了高达 18 亿欧元的减值损失。</p>\n  <p>面对如此沉重的财务包袱，新任保时捷首席执行官 Michael Leiters 也不得不定下「削减冗余开发支出」的铁腕计划。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657530\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-5.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2788\" height=\"1628\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-5.png!720 2788w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-5-360x210.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-5-768x448.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/6-5-1024x598.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2788px) 100vw, 2788px\"></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲ 新任保时捷 CEO&nbsp;Michael Leiters</p>\n  </div>\n  <h2><strong>同名异体</strong></h2>\n  <p>好在保时捷并不打算直接停产其中一款车型，而是倾向于采用「同名异体」的整合方式，即用单一产品线名称同时覆盖不同平台和动力形式，同时提供燃油、插混和纯电三种选项。</p>\n  <p>这种做法在保时捷内部并不陌生。目前，Macan 与 Cayenne 的燃油版和纯电版已在多个市场并行销售，尽管它们基于完全不同的平台打造。</p>\n  <p>如果保时捷将将这套逻辑延伸至轿车产品线，那么大致方向也会是，燃油及插混版本采用 PPC 平台，纯电版本采用 SSP Sport 平台，而对外统一呈现为单一产品线。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657532\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-4.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2788\" height=\"1628\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-4.png!720 2788w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-4-360x210.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-4-768x448.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/7-4-1024x598.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2788px) 100vw, 2788px\"></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲ 目前大众旗下的各类平台</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>据 Autocar 等外媒报道，保时捷目前正在探索更大范围的零部件共享，以及建立共同产品标识的可能性，即便后续车型仍继续使用不同的底层平台。</p>\n  <p>为了将降本增效推向极致，保时捷的工程师们正在寻求跨越现有底盘架构的通用化方案。即便未来的产品线依然建立在两套不同的底盘架构上，保时捷也力求在电子电气架构、车机信息娱乐系统的底层代码、座椅总成骨架、空调温控模块，甚至是最能代表保时捷操控灵魂的 Porsche Active Ride 主动悬挂技术上，实现跨平台的模块化大规模共享。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657533\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-2.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2038\" height=\"1150\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-2.png!720 2038w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-2-360x203.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-2-768x433.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/8-2-1024x578.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2038px) 100vw, 2038px\"></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲orsche Active Ride 主动悬挂技术</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>除了底盘架构外，若两款车最终走向产品线合并，外观设计和车身形态的整合将是另一道难题。</p>\n  <p>目前这两款车的视觉特征存在着显著的性格撕裂。</p>\n  <p>Taycan 受益于纯电动架构带来的物理优势，重心被压得极低，整体姿态紧凑且充满战斗气息，空气动力学设计极具侵略性。</p>\n  <p>而 Panamera 则是一台标准的旗舰四门房车，拥有更加修长、宽厚的身形，呈现出经典豪华车从容不迫的巡航气场。</p>\n  <p>此外，一旦轿车产品线走向合并，为了尽最大可能精简复杂的生产线并降低制造成本，类似 Taycan Cross Turismo 这种研发成本高昂但受众极其狭窄的旅行车变体，大概率将面临被无情砍掉的命运。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657534\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-3.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2236\" height=\"1270\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-3.png!720 2236w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-3-360x204.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-3-768x436.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/9-3-1024x582.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2236px) 100vw, 2236px\"></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲Taycan Cross Turismo</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>在视觉特征的最终呈现上，业界普遍推测保时捷极有可能再次参考新款 Cayenne 的做法。</p>\n  <p>即在统一的家族化车身轮廓和内饰布局下，允许燃油版和纯电版车型保留各自专属的前脸格栅样式、进气口造型以及特定的空气动力学细节。</p>\n  <p>这样一来，消费者只需扫一眼车头，便能清晰地辨识其内部运转的是内燃机还是电机，同时也让纯电版车型能够藉此保留一丝 Taycan 曾经引以为傲的科幻视觉基因。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657535\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-1.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2822\" height=\"1542\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-1.png!720 2822w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-1-360x197.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-1-768x420.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/10-1-1024x560.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2822px) 100vw, 2822px\"></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲ 纯电卡宴</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>至于合并后沿用哪个名字——Panamera 还是 Taycan——目前在保时捷高层会议上仍是一个悬而未决的焦灼点。</p>\n  <p>「Panamera」 这个名字无疑拥有着更深厚的全球基本盘、更庞大的高净值车主群体以及燃油车时代不可磨灭的辉煌记忆；但 「Taycan」 毕竟代表了保时捷劈开电动时代的第一把利刃，承载了品牌向新世纪转型的决绝与锐气。</p>\n  <p>抹去其中任何一个，都是一种遗憾与损失。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657536\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-2.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2822\" height=\"1542\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-2.png!720 2822w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-2-360x197.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-2-768x420.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/11-2-1024x560.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2822px) 100vw, 2822px\"></p>\n  <div class=\"editor-image-source\">\n   <p>▲ 初代帕美</p>\n  </div>\n  <p>幸运的是，在最终判决下达之前，保时捷还有一点时间。</p>\n  <p>第三代 Panamera 刚于 2023 年底完成首发，而 Taycan 也已在 2024 年进行了大规模的中期改款。按照传统豪华车企通常长达七到八年的迭代节奏，这两款车的彻底换代节点将落在 2029 至 2030 年左右。</p>\n  <p>这意味着保时捷目前仍有相对充裕的时间来完成平台整合方案的论证和工程布局，在正式替代方案落地之前，两款现款车型仍将各自独立运作。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1657537\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-2.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2822\" height=\"1542\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-2.png!720 2822w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-2-360x197.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-2-768x420.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/12-2-1024x560.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2822px) 100vw, 2822px\"></p>\n  <p>回望 2019 年尼亚加拉瀑布前的那个清晨，Taycan 曾被无数人视作保时捷通向未来的开始。</p>\n  <p>而在经历了电气化初期的狂飙突进后，在高端纯电性能车遇冷、插电混动技术强势回潮的大背景下，用更为集约高效的<span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, \\&quot;Heiti SC\\&quot;, STHeiti, SimHei, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;white-space: normal;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration: none;text-decoration-thickness: auto;text-decoration-style: solid;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 27px 0px;padding: 0px 15px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);text-align: justify;line-height: 25px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">研发方式</span>去覆盖尽可能全面的动力矩阵，或许是这家巨头所能做出的最清醒的防守反击了。</p>\n </body>\n</html>",
